   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## 1. The Scene and environment basics\n", "This runs our smoke test script: launches Isaac Sim, creates the Franka Lift task, prints the Scene entities (robot, object, ee_frame), observation/action spaces, and steps with random actions."]
